pid":"71ab8bce12b045255347e2ddb8dfa50716a62e71","tid":496060,"uid":113776,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T01:32:03.000Z","msg":"ON9...任何動物都唔會同自己有壞既生物生活喺同一個空間。<br />\n關蝴蝶咩事，相反喺甲蟲金龜呢類差不多樣既多數人都會唔會打，因為知對自己無壞。"},{"pid":"195debdcac7df5cdfe91966696d6986bf8bbb180","tid":496060,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T01:33:22.000Z","msg":"因為蝴蝶食花蜜，曱甴就食我食既嘢食"},{"pid":"3c859b7bcf77c839c483517faa7c2da65fb7469e","tid":496060,"uid":49163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T01:34:59.000Z","msg":"我會追撚住d蝴蝶黎斬"},{"pid":"1c09d3fc2ae11d7289e42c71562abefd42fd1069","tid":496060,"uid":32586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T01:35:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解食豬食牛，唔食狗？</blockquote><br />\n返大陸食"},{"pid":"93e258f32de6ca592a29f55cbe5e842bf5dcafd7","tid":496060,"uid":9887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T01:36:37.000Z","msg":"靚女同醜女待遇都大不同啦<br />\n連登仔應該好明白<br />\n咁鍾意靚既蝴蝶殺醜既曱甴又有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de44be35a2bebd66caf2cd0c1b0aaeb51d318a8f","tid":496060,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T01:38:21.000Z","msg":"由的做起養蟑螂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"754909a7e514f2d69fd1e119f0ed866e23fe252c","tid":496060,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T01:40:19.000Z","msg":"見親蝴蝶都殺"},{"pid":"546a3292fe6dc1914f24d85cd5321d78d1b0dda4","tid":496060,"uid":134474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T01:41:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好撚驚+好撚憎蝴蝶<br />\n見到就想用火槍噴鳩佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n越大隻越多花紋既 越恐怖<br />\n飛埋黎 我會起哂雞皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n殺小強係因為驚佢有菌<br />\n殺蝴蝶/飛蛾 係因為我好撚驚佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n成雙成對嗰啲仆街蝴蝶先恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 嗰次行山嚇到我差啲碌落山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我俾小強爬過幾次腳，有一次仲從天而降跌咗落我個頭到爬咗成十分鐘先發現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但都無咁憎佢地<br />\n<br />\n反而蝴蝶我試過俾佢地嚇到差啲喊出嚟，真係好討厭<br />\n<br />\n利申藍屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4455cf50a9419dc07772d6a3caaa52610c055961","tid":496060,"uid":20072,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T01:47:18.000Z","msg":"蟑螂算唔算蝗語？ <br />\n正常香港人叫開甲由/小強"},{"pid":"6006f3bf990b071f30cc7867c50a1c3065109dc8","tid":496060,"uid":99048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T01:47:30.000Z","msg":"樓豬仲相信公平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n老實講信有公平同信有耶穌冇分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50fc529f47285e7ec4f023cd7b84b9bd14c433ed","tid":496060,"uid":17263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T01:52:19.000Z","msg":"蝴蝶飛蛾同曱甴都好核突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n打字都起雞皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a84673988305580b100f8081a0b16430f7d09f28","tid":496060,"uid":69013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T01:54:35.000Z","msg":"大自然一向物競天擇<br />\n因為自己係生命，所以要同其他物種競爭，對於蟑螂等害蟲，因為會散播病菌危害人類健康，所以要除害。不過切記，除害要最低限度的除害，不是濫殺，亦不是以此為樂。我個人唔支持用殺蟲水，因為中毒的昆蟲有機會被其他捕獵者誤食而中毒，會誤殺其他非與人類直接競爭既生物。<br />\n唔追殺蝴蝶，因為佢地無與人類直接競爭，亦係散播病菌，基於人類道德責任，不應該濫殺「無辜」，所以唔應該殺佢地。<br />\nBtw, 樓主幾歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1c2578fdc6393747fcb75362cab776a0a18b00c","tid":496060,"uid":69013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T01:56:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>蟑螂算唔算蝗語？ <br />\n正常香港人叫開甲由/小強</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n書面語 vs 蝗語"},{"pid":"e8a84b595a1b1db1fba876af10c619eb02a9679e","tid":496060,"uid":161243,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T01:56:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>眾生是平等的，昆蟲亦一樣<br />\n<br />\n無人一出世就鐘意做蟑螂<br />\n<br />\n而係一個無罪假定既社會下，點解人類往往要未審先判地判蟑螂死刑？相反你地一見係蝴蝶唔單至唔殺，仲要保䕶影相打卡？有無人可憐下蟑螂？<br />\n<br />\n唔好同我講因為蟑螂污漕樣衰乜乜柒柒，眾生是平等可容許有高低尚之分嗎？<br />\n<br />\n點解人類唔能夠將看待蟑螂與看待蝴蝶睇齊？<br />\n<br />\n利申：文明左冀民主分子</blockquote><br />\non撚9.<br />\n生物能繁衍下去, 先要保護自己族群生存權。<br />\n蟑螂成億成萬; 威脅人類生存, 你唔打撚死佢, 佢霸佔埋你生存空間;<br />\n蝴蝶無法係城市繁衍, 人類不視為威脅, 你才有心思保䕶佢 (我好撚憎蝴蝶, 核撚故,不視生產,對ecosystem冇貢獻);<br />\n物競天擇, 物種存在非必然, 人類能幸存, 全憑心狠手辣;<br />\n別以為人類好高尚, 也只衣冠禽獸。<br />\n若人類不夠心狠手辣, 早已絕滅, 你死撚左變左靈魂再講乜柒眾生平等<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d760da5db9195c72d8737aa4250d16ff368be86a","tid":496060,"uid":52595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T01:59:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8d2e48e12991ff704d4994f852f943125927f2ee","tid":496060,"uid":123579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T02:25:18.000Z","msg":"我就好公平見咩蟲都殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c905901d7bfaf1cc6bb7d50fbe3d82601d80a617","tid":496060,"uid":100391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T03:13:00.000Z","msg":"蝴蝶唔會飛入我間屋同食我啲野食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  關我撚事咩<br />\n人不犯我 我不犯人"}]}